  <description><![CDATA[<p>Sitting in a perfect ski-in/ski-out position in <a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" title="Val d'Isere">Val d'Isère</a>, with a fantastic spa and swimming pool, we're very excited about this 5* residence! The apartments are all spacious and luxuriously decorated with stylish interiors. It is ideal for families, with its child friendly swimming pool including aquatic games and a fun area. </p>
<h2>Cosy and chic</h2>
<p><span>The chalet apartments are spacious, and equipped with everything you may need for a self-catered stay in the Alps - each of the apartments are furnished to a high standard combining traditional wood with modern amenities. They all have their own equipped kitchen, so you can choose to stay in and enjoy home cooked meals or venture out and sample some of the popular restaurants in the resort centre. </span></p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>Chalet Izia has a fantastic location in <a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" title="Val d'Isere">Val d'Isere,</a> with ski-in and ski-out access, <span>allowing you to reach the slopes with ease each day. Beginners as well as more experienced skiers will particularly enjoy the vast amount of slopes in the area, from cruisy blues to steep blacks - there is something for everyone in <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes-Val d'Isere.</a></span></p>
<h2>Relax and unwind </h2>
<p><span>After a day of exploring the slopes, make the most of the indoor swimming pool, whirlpool bath, sauna and hammam. A range of treatments and massages are available to book locally - perfect for a moment of pure relaxation and soothing any achy ski legs. </span></p>
<h2><span>Family friendly</span></h2>
<p><span>The Chalets Izia is </span>designed around families, there is an unsupervised <span>children’s area in the lobby with a reading corner and playroom. Plus the beauty centre offers special treatments for children - a wonderful way for the younger ones to experience the spa and wellness centre. Access to the slopes is also really easy with the ski school meeting point and chair lifts being a short walk away, great for new skiers and boarders looking for convenient access to the slopes.</span></p>]]></description>
