  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Two bedroom apartments</strong> sleep two to four people and are around 60m². These apartments have an open-plan kitchen, living room and two bedrooms with en-suite bathrooms.</p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom fireplace apartments</strong> sleep two to four people and are around 60m². These apartments have an open-plan kitchen,  living room with a fireplace and two bedrooms with en-suite bathrooms.</p>
<p><strong>Three bedroom apartments</strong> sleep four to six people and are around 80m². These apartments have an open-plan kitchen and living room, and three twin bedrooms with their own en-suite bathrooms with a shower room.</p>
<p><strong>Four bedroom apartments</strong> sleep four to eight people and are around 135m². These apartments have an open-plan kitchen and living room, and four twin bedrooms with their own en-suite bathrooms. <span>This apartment may be on one level or duplex.</span></p>
<p>Beds are made on arrival, a mid week towel change is available on request and end of week cleaning is included (except the kitchen and bins).</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Balcony or terrace with furniture</li>
<li>Mountain views</li>
<li>Lounge area</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Telephone</li>
<li>Bathrobes and slippers</li>
<li>Fully equipped <span>kitchen with hob, oven, microwave, extractor fan, refrigerator with freezer compartment, dishwasher, coffee maker Nespresso, kettle, toaster, pressure cooker, blender and kitchenware</span></li>
<li>Cleaning kit</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>End of stay cleaning is included except the kitchen. Bins must also be taken out.</li>
<li>Additional beds are available for a supplement</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
